        <br />
        <p>The ceremony, dinner and reception will be held at the same venue, Punta Barranca. When you arrive at 8pm, you'll be greeted with beer, wine and champagne. After a brief ceremony at 8:30pm, we'll kick off the celebration with more drinks and passed appetizers.</p>
        <p>The ceremony and cocktail hour will be outside on the grass veranda overlooking the Parana River (don't forget, February in Argentina is summertime :-)). During this time, you'll be able to watch the dinner food being cooked in one of the large outdoor Asados. It's quite the sight to see!</p>
      </div>
