        <p>Around 10pm, we'll head inside for a sit down Asado dinner. For your carnivores, this mean meat, meat & more meat. For the non-meat eaters, don't worry, we will have lots great veggie and fish options for you.</p> 
        <p>After dinner, we'll enjoy some desserts and then head to the dance floor for a night of dancing - to a live band and a fun DJ. In true Argentinian fashion, we'll be partying until 6am and serving up some breakfast before then to keep you nice and nourished! </p>
